# The Trunk capsules (hey-social, hey-chat) ship their PRE-BUILT bundle in the
# git tarball: runtime-ynh's deploy flattens the COMMITTED dist/* into the
# capsule root with NO on-server trunk build (_common.sh: "was dist/ left
# gitignored (it must be force-added)?"). So track the hashed wasm/js + the
# html/css, but keep build cruft (.stage, snippets, source maps) out.
capsules/*/dist/*
!capsules/*/dist/*.wasm
!capsules/*/dist/*.js
!capsules/*/dist/*.html
!capsules/*/dist/*.css
